# Frontend Environment Variables Example

## Development Environment (.env.development)
REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

## Staging Environment (.env.staging)
REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL=https://deknek-backend-staging.vercel.app/api

## Production Environment (.env.production)
REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL=https://deknek-backend.vercel.app/api

## Local Testing
REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

## Vercel Production
REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL=https://your-backend-url.vercel.app/api
